insert into CET6WordBook values ('212', 'Catholic', '[kæθəlɪk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=Catholic', '{adj.}++天主教的**++罗马天主教的**++正教的**++天主教教徒的**{n.}++天主教教徒**++罗马天主教教徒**++普世性基督教教徒**++英国国教高教派**++[美国俚语]扒手**{adj.}++(范围或涵义)一般的；普遍的，广泛的**++宽容的，宽宏大量的，气量大的**', '++He was a Catholic but didn@t practise his religion.**++他那时是天主教徒，但并不实践信仰。**++But first, you have to be single and you must be Catholic.**++但首先你必须是单身的且你必须是天主教徒。**++James,my son,you are a Protestant and I am a Catholic.**++詹姆斯，我的儿子，你是个新教徒而我是个天主教徒。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('213', 'caution', '[kɔʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=caution', '{n.}++小心，谨慎**++警告；告诫；劝告**++警告 (或告诫) 的言词(或表示)**++[美国口语] 引人注目的人 (或物)**{vt.}++劝…谨慎小心；警告，告诫：**++劝…谨慎小心；警告，告诫：**', '++There is no need for such caution.**++不必如此小心谨慎。**++Due caution should be exercised in discriminating between the two.**++在区别这两者时应该相当谨慎。**++All reports emanating from that country should be treated with caution.**++所有来自那个国家的报告都应谨慎处理。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('214', 'cautious', '[kɔʃəs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=cautious', '{adj.}', '++I have to be very cautious in what I say about abortion.**++这位候选人说：我在讲人工流产的问题上必须十分谨慎。**++He was even more cautious than ever, and did his utmost to win the trust and favour of the superior.**++他更加谨小慎微， 兢兢业业， 以尽力取信讨好其上司。**++You should be cautious of these distractions, but allow yourself the occasional distraction to break up your day.**++对于这些让人分心的事物你应该谨慎，但是你也要允许自己偶尔的分心去分解你的一天。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('215', 'cavity', '[kævəti]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=cavity', '{n.}++洞，穴，中空，凹处，槽，模槽；弹腔**++【解剖学】腔，(空) 洞，盂**++【医学】牙腔，蛀牙的洞**++【电子学】空腔共振器，谐振器**', '++Heart transplants were once considered immoral–how could you open the chest cavity of one person and transplant the heart into the body of another person?**++心脏移植曾经一度被认为是不道德的——你怎么可以在一个人的胸部开个洞，然后把心脏移植到另外一个人的身体里呢？**++Ultraviolet radiation and violent stellar winds have blown out an enormous cavity in the gas and dust enveloping the cluster, providing an unobstructed view of the cluster.**++紫外线和猛烈的星际风，在气体以及包裹星群的灰尘上吹出了一个硕大的洞，（为人类）提供了一个畅通无阻的观察星群的视野。**++The external cavity quantum cascade laser with this design may operate very stable due to its low dependences on voltage and temperature,  he says.**++“应用这种设计的外腔式量子级联激光器能够非常稳定地运行，这得益于对电压和温度的弱依赖关系，”他说。**');
