insert into CET6WordBook values ('318', 'confidential', '[,kɑnfɪdɛnʃl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=confidential', '{adj.}++机密的，秘密的**++表示信任的，表示亲密的，知心的**++获得信任的；参与机密的**', '++We mustn@t allow such a person access to confidential matters of the state.**++不能让这样的人与闻国家机密。**++You mentioned measurable benefits - are you able to share some of these with us or is that confidential?**++你提到了可测量的收益——你能和我们分享一下具体情况吗？ 这是机密吗？**++The incident highlights how easy it can be for anyone with access to confidential information stored online to abuse it, regardless of any systems that are in place.**++这一事件凸显了，不论是在任何系统，任何地方，储存在网上的机密资料被有机会接触到它们的人滥用是多么的容易。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('319', 'confirmation', '[,kɑnfɚmeʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=confirmation', '{n.}++(进一步)确定，确立；证实**++确认，批准**++证据，确证，证明**++【基督教】坚信礼，坚振礼，按手礼 **++【犹太教】(对年轻人所行的)坚信礼**', '++This week you finally have confirmation.**++这一周你最终确认了这点。**++As of this morning, we do have that confirmation.**++今天早上，我们确实得到了伊朗方面的证实。**++They say this should help her in the confirmation process.**++他们认为这将对她在确认提名过程中更为有利。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('320', 'conform', '[kənfɔrm]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=conform', '{vi.}++遵照；适应；顺从，一致(常与to 连用)：**++符合；相似(常与with连用)：**++【历史】遵奉国教会(指英国国教会)惯例**{vt.}++使符合，使一致；使相似：**++使顺应；使协调；使遵照：**{adj.}++[古语]一致的，相似的**', '++It@s not just humans, there@s evidence that chimps conform as well.**++不仅限于人类，也有证据表明黑猩猩也符合这项理论。**++If you disagree and don’t conform to their expectations, some of them get confused or irritated.**++如果你不同意或者和他们期望的不一致，他们中的一些人就会困惑生气。**++These must be in the best interest of the enterprise and also conform to applicable laws and regulations.**++这些计划必须是为了企业利益最大化，并且符合需要遵从的法律及规章制度。**');
