insert into CET6WordBook values ('897', 'impurity', '[ɪmpjʊrəti]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=impurity', '{n.}++不纯，不洁；掺杂，掺假**++[常用复数]不纯之物，不洁之物；杂质；污染物**++不道德；猥亵；亵渎；渎神**++【物理学】杂质(原子)**', '++What are these sources of impurity?**++不纯洁的来源又是什么呢？**++It symbolizes the victory of the forces of life, oath and holiness over death and impurity.**++这象征着生命力的胜利，誓言和神圣能够战胜死亡和不洁。**++In very severe cases, it can even defile some common objects, and in those cases, the source of impurity might have to be isolated or excluded if necessary.**++在一些非常严峻的情况中，它会玷污一些普通的事物，在这种时候，不洁之源,也许只能被孤立，严重的话需要驱逐。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('898', 'inaccessible', '[,ɪnæksɛsəbl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=inaccessible', '{adj.}++达不到的，难达到的；进不去的**++不易(或不可)接近的；不易(或不能)见到的；不受影响的；难打交道的**++得不到的，难得到的**++难懂的，无法理解的**', '++I had been perceived as being inaccessible then, in part because I accepted so many daytime speaking engagements out in the state.**++那时候，我被认为是一个难以接近的人，部分是因为白天我接受了很多邀请，到全州各地发表演说。**++In the latter case, that role will not match any users and the interface might be inaccessible.**++在后一种情况下，这个角色不与任何用户匹配，接口就是不可访问的。**++Affected queues can fill up with messages that are currently inaccessible while other applications or tasks might be waiting to get these messages.**++受影响的队列会充满当前无法访问的消息，而其他应用程序或任务可能正在等待获取这些消息。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('899', 'inaccurate', '[ɪnækjərət]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=inaccurate', '{adj.}++不准确的，不精确的**++错误的；不真实的**', '++This is a silly and inaccurate way to think about time, however.**++然而，这是一种愚蠢和错误的看待时间的方法。**++It’s very difficult to achieve a goal that’s based on an inaccurate model of reality — such a goal will surely be an uphill struggle.**++要实现一个建立在错误的现实模型基础上的目标是相当困难的-达到这样的目标无异于做无谓的挣扎。**++It could also be an invalidation notice specifying that part of data should not be considered in the integration process because it is inaccurate.**++它经常是一个无效的通告，部分的数据集成过程中应该不会被考虑，因为他们是错误的。**');
