insert into CET6WordBook values ('959', 'instantaneous', '[,ɪnstəntenɪəs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=instantaneous', '{adj.}++即刻的；瞬间的**++猝然的；猝发的**++【物理学】瞬时的，即时的**', '++Only then can the user manipulate the data with the near instantaneous response of a true local application.**++只有在这时，用户才能真正以本地应用程序接近即时响应的速度来处理数据。**++The true test, then, of the radical spirit, is the button-pushing test: if we could push the button for instantaneous abolition of unjust invasions of liberty, would we do it?**++那么，对真正的激进精神的测试就是这个按钮测试：假如我们按下按钮就能够瞬间废除所有非正义的对自由的侵犯，我们会这样做吗？**++In today’s media world, not only is feedback instantaneous. Anyone with an Internet connection can be a publisher, can raise their voice, can tell the world what they see and what they think.**++在现今的媒体世界，不仅读者反馈是即时的，任何人都可以通过因特网接入成为出版者，可以大声表达意见，可以告诉世界自己的所见所想。**');
