insert into CET6WordBook values ('1011', 'kinetic', '[kɪnɛtɪk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=kinetic', '{adj.}++【物理学】运动的；动力的；运动引起的**++活跃的；有力的；有生气的**++活动艺术的，动态艺术的**', '++Typing helps activate the kinetic part of your brain that helps improve learning through physical activity.**++打字可以帮助激活你大脑中运动的部分，这有助于从生理行为方面促进学习。**++The boots work by capturing the heat of the wearer@s feet -- not kinetic energy, like other walking-power concepts we@ve seen.**++发电长筒靴通过吸收脚部热量工作——而不像我们以前看过的创意那样，利用行走、运动产生能量。**++With each collision, they dump more of their kinetic energy into the massive column—trying vainly to make it swing like a pendulum.**++他们通过每一次碰撞，将运动产生的能量传给巨大的柱子—像个摆锤一样释放所有的能量。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1012', 'kit', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=kit', '{n.}++成套工具(或用具、物件设备) **++(供组装用的)成套配件，配套元件**++成套用品，(旅行等用的)行装**{vt.}++装备，配备(常与out， up连用):**++使穿戴，打扮(常与up连用):**{vi.}++被装备 (常与out， up连用)**{n.}++小猫 (= kitten)**++小狐，软毛小动物**++软毛小动物的毛皮**{n.}', '++Every household should assemble a disaster supplies kit and keep it up to date.**++每个家庭都应该备有一套灾难用品装备并一直留存。**++Dedicate a small shelf or a drawer to lunch things and kit it out with the basics.**++贡献出一个小架子或一个抽屉来装午餐材料，将所需的基本用品装备齐全。**++Your kit should be waterproof as well, particularly if you will travel with it away from home; however, sealing your supplies inside of zipper baggies is usually all you need to do the job.**++你的急救工具箱还必须是防水的，尤其是当你带着它出门远行的时候；不过，你通常需要密封拉链袋里面的用品。**');
