insert into CET6WordBook values ('1028', 'lengthen', '[lɛŋθən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=lengthen', '{vt.}++放长，加长；使变长；使伸长；使延长：**++【语音学】拖长(元音)音长**{vi.}++变长，延伸，长起来：**++变长，延伸，长起来：**', '++The teacher told her to lengthen her paper out.**++老师让她把论文加长。**++It is deep enough. She begins to widen, lengthen and shape the trench.**++已足够深了，她开始将它扩展、延长并做成想要的样子。**++As lifespans lengthen, a person could still retire at, say, 66, but with a smaller annual benefit.**++因为寿命延长，所以人们能在66岁退休，但获得相对少一些的年薪。**');
