insert into CET6WordBook values ('1171', 'multiplication', '[mʌltəpləkeʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=multiplication', '{n.}++增加，增多；倍增**++【数学】乘法；乘法运算**++【电工学】增殖**', '++The teacher drilled grammar and the multiplication tables every day.**++教员每天通过练习传授语法和乘法表。**++But what I do? I just separated, do I do the addition first or do the multiplication first?**++那么我该怎么办？我就是要做一个分割，应该先做加法呢,是先做乘法呢？**++And we can reformulate this in terms of matrix multiplication or matrix product.**++我们可以用,矩阵乘法或矩阵乘积的形式来表述这些式子。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1172', 'multitude', '[mʌltɪˌtud, -ˌtjud]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=multitude', '{n.}++许多，大量，众多；众多状态**++大群人；大批**++[the multitude(s)]群众,大众**', '++This is Pharaoh and all his multitude, saith the Lord GOD.**++法老和他的群众乃是如此。 这是主耶和华说的。**++So the term “middle class” covers a multitude of differences.**++因此，“中产阶级”这个术语涵盖了众多的差异。**++They had not lived in every conceivable manner, far from it, but what room would there be for the multitude if each individual tried to exhaust the permutations of existence?**++他们并没有体验过所有可能的生活方式，远远没有；但是，如果每人都试图体验所有的可能的生活方式，芸芸众生又将如何自处？**');
