insert into CET6WordBook values ('1322', 'perfection', '[pɚfɛkʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=perfection', '{n.}++完成；改善；完满**++完整无缺；无比精确；尽善尽美；登峰造极**++[复数]才艺；造诣；优点；成就**++理想的人(或物)；完美的典型**++完全；极端；绝对**', '++And she did so with grace and perfection!**++而她做的非常优雅和完美！**++Absolute perfection in a dictionary is rare.**++绝对完美的词典是罕见的。**++It was little by little that the watch reached its present-day perfection.**++表渐渐地达到了现在这样完美的程度。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1323', 'peril', '[pɛrəl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=peril', '{n.}++(严重的)危险；冒险；险因**++危险的事物；(可能导致犯罪的)危险行为**++险情；险境；风险**{vt.}++置…于危险中；冒险：**++置…于危险中；冒险：**', '++We believe this at our peril.**++我们相信这个是危险的。**++The past made us what we are now, and we forget it at our peril.**++过去造就了我们现在的样子，我们忘掉它是危险的。**++But as with the Holocaust, if we forget, we do so at great peril to our own humanity.**++但是与大屠杀一样，如果我们遗忘它，那么我们就会冒着重复它极大的危险。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1324', 'perimeter', '[pərɪmɪtɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=perimeter', '{n.}++周，周围；边缘**++周长；周边**++【军事】 (兵营或工事的) 环形防线；防御带**++【医学】视野计**', '++A fence marked the perimeter of the field.**++一道篱笆标明了那块田地的周界。**++If you have a HVAC unit, your condenser is outside on the perimeter of your house.**++如果你有一个制热空调，那你的制冷器就在房子外部周边地区。**++But let me not go too far in suggesting that asset classes near the perimeter of risk have no future.**++但我还是得讲得审慎点，免得大家以为我在暗示风险较高的资产类别全无前途。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1325', 'periodic', '[,pɪrɪɑdɪk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=periodic', '{adj.}++定期的；一定时期的；定时的**++回归的；间歇的，时而发生的**++周期的；循环的**++【数学】周期函数的**++【语法学】用尾重句的；用圆周句的**++(古希腊语系中)格律群的**++美丽词句的**{adj.}', '++This periodic use of snapshots can be especially useful in detecting trends.**++在探测趋势时，这种定期使用快照的方法特别有用。**++If you happen to find this approach successful, please let us know so that we can plan periodic updates for future columns.**++如果您碰巧发现这种方法很成功，请告诉我们，以便我们能够为今后的专栏计划定期的更新。**++One way to deal with trash is periodic cleaning: Every once in a while we assemble a crew to go out and pick up trash as thoroughly as our budget permits.**++处理垃圾的一种方法是定期清理：每一次当我们聚集在一船员走出去，拿起了彻底垃圾作为我们预算许可。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1326', 'periodical', '[,pɪrɪɑdɪkl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=periodical', '{adj.}++=periodic**++定期刊行的**++期刊的**{n.}++期刊，杂志**', '++She refereed for a periodical a few years ago.**++几年前她为一期刊担任编审。**++The quarterly magazine is a periodical published every three months.**++季刊是每3个月出版一次的期刊。**++As the flagship periodical of the World Health Organization (WHO), the Bulletin draws on WHO experts as editorial advisers, reviewers and authors as well as on external collaborators.**++作为世界卫生组织（世卫组织）的主要期刊，《简报》利用世卫组织专家与外部合作者担任编辑顾问、评审人和作者。**');
