insert into CET6WordBook values ('1328', 'perish', '[pɛrɪʃ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=perish', '{vi.}++枯萎；凋谢：**++灭亡；消灭：**++死去(尤指暴卒、夭折)：**++(食物等)腐败；腐烂；(橡胶、皮革等)硬化毁坏：**{vt.}++消灭；杀死；使死去：**++毁坏；毁损：**++[常用被动语态]使非常困苦；使麻木：**{n.}++[澳大利亚口语]濒临死亡的贫困状态**', '++But estimates of their ages depend on theories of how stars live and perish.**++不过，估计它们的年龄取决于恒星如何生存与死亡的理论。**++“If I couldn@t walk fast and far”, he once said, “I think I should explode and perish.**++“如果我不能走得快又远，”他曾经说道，“我想我应该爆炸，然后腐烂。”**++"Publish or perish" is the traditional saying.**++“发表或毁灭”是传统的说法。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1329', 'perpendicular', '[pɝpəndɪkjəlɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=perpendicular', '{adj.}++成直角的；正交的；垂直的**++矗立的；体态笔直的**++险陡的；陡立的；陡峭的**++贯穿不同类型(或层次)的；由不同类型(或层次)组成的**++社会式的**++[P-]【建筑学】垂直式的**{n.}++垂规；铅垂线**++垂直线；垂直面**++垂直；垂线**++直立；直立姿势**++陡坡；峭壁**++正直；刚正**++[P-]垂直式建筑**++[俚语]站着进餐**', '++It was straight, correct, cold, perpendicular, levelled with the square, laid out by rule and line.**++它笔直、整齐、冷酷、垂直，是用角尺、拉线和铅锤来达到这一平正和划一的。**++A severe facade rose above this door; a wall, perpendicular to the facade, almost touched the door, and flanked it with an abrupt right angle.**++大门的上方便是那房屋的正面，气象庄严，一道和房屋正面垂直的墙紧靠在大门旁边，构成一个生硬的直角。**++The researchers found that if they stretched out the substance in a second direction perpendicular to the first, it could then be stretched in any direction without harm.**++研究人员发现，如果向着第一次拉伸的垂直方向拉扯，它仍然能够向着任何方向毫无损害地任意伸展。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1330', 'perpetual', '[pɚpɛtʃuəl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=perpetual', '{adj.}++永远的；永恒的；长期的**++(职位)终身的；无限期的**++不断的；重复不停的**++(投资)永不还本的**++四季花开的；连续开花的**++连绵不绝的；不断的**++[口语]无休止的；连续不断的**{n.}++多年生植物(尤指四季开花的蔷薇)；多年生草**++永不还本的投资**', '++They hoped to live in perpetual happiness.**++他们希望生活在永久幸福之中.**++To be empty of thought, of goals, of ambition, of perpetual motion or entertainment.**++没有想法，没有目标，没有野心，也没有不断的运动或者娱乐。**++But the true sign of success is not whether we are a source of perpetual aid that helps people scrape by — it’s whether we are partners in building the capacity of transformational change.**++但成功的真正标志，不在于我们是否是一个帮人勉强度日的永久的援助源泉，而在于我们是否是一个为实现改天换地的变化而进行能力建设的伙伴。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1331', 'perplex', '[pɚplɛks]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=perplex', '{vt.}++使困惑；使难住；使茫然；使费解：**++使复杂化；使纠缠不清；使难办：**{n.}++[古语]= perplexity**', '++But don’t perplex the issue; it isn’t so complicated.**++但不要使问题复杂化了。 它没有那么复杂。**++Putin\@s rise continues to perplex even devoted Kremlin observers.**++普京的崛起至今让克林姆林宫的观察家们感到迷惑。**++But these potentially anonymous weapons continue to perplex and confound our thinking about the future of war and terrorism.**++但是，这些潜在的不为人知的武器继续困扰着我们，并影响着我们对于未来战争和恐怖主义的看法。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1332', 'persecute', '[pɝsɪkjut]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=persecute', '{vt.}++(尤指因政治、种族、宗教信仰不同而引起的)迫害；残害；虐待：**++困扰；为难：**++跟…纠缠；同…捣乱：**++[主英国英语]依法执行**', '++Persecute me!**++迫害我吧！**++They persecute those who do not conform to their ideas.**++他们迫害那些不符合他们意见的人。**++If it comes to burning somebody at the stake for not believing it, then it is worth while to remember that after all he may be right, and it is not worth while to persecute him.**++如果仅仅因为一个人不相信（某件事情），便把他绑到火刑柱上，那么这就很值得去记住毕竟他很可能是对的，（因而）不值得去迫害他。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1333', 'persevere', '[,pɝsəvɪr]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=persevere', '{vi.}++坚持；不屈不挠；坚忍：**++(辩论中)固执己见：**++[古语]持续；保持**{vt.}++支持；支撑；鼓舞：**++支持；支撑；鼓舞：**', '++Persevere and you@ll succeed.**++只要你坚持不懈， 你自会成功。**++If you persevere at your search for a job, you are sure to find something suitable in the end.**++如果你坚持找工作，最后，你肯定会找到合适的工作。**++If you are struggling with this technique, then persevere.**++如果你正在尝试这种方法，那么坚持下去。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1334', 'persist', '[pɚsɪst]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=persist', '{vi.}++坚持；固持；坚持不懈；始终：**++重(复)申(说)；主张；追问；坚称：**++持续；持久；存留：**', '++But you must persist.**++但是你必须坚持。**++I say no at first, but they persist. They promise to work around my schedule; they flatter me.**++一开始我说“不”，但是对方坚持，保证按我的日程安排，还奉承我，对我说，“我们需要你！”**++So persist until your stars align and god opens the path for you.**++因此坚持，直到你的星排成一条直线，直到上帝为你开放这条道路。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1335', 'persistence', '[pɚsɪstəns]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=persistence', '{n.}++坚持；固执；顽固**++持久性;韧性;持续状态;存留(状态) [亦作 persistency ／pəsistənsi,-zis-／]**++持续；存留**', '++So we need a persistence mechanism to store the new object data.**++所以我们需要一个持续机制来存储新的对象数据。**++In the case of persistence, for instance, you probably should create a "persistence layer" in your application.**++例如，在持续的情况下，您可能应该在应用程序中创建一个“持续层”。**++In analysis we need only to specify a meaningful name for the persistence store, but the details of how we achieve this persistence will be addressed later in design.**++在分析阶段我们只需要为持续存储指定一个有意义的名字，而如何实现这个持续性的细节将在后面的设计阶段解决。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1336', 'personality', '[,pɝsənæləti]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=personality', '{n.}++个人的存在；个人；人物；名人**++个性；性格；人的特征**++(团体、国家、地方)独有的特性**++品格；人格；对性格总的印象**++[常作复数]人物批评；人身攻击；攻击个人(的材料)**++[常作复数]人物评议；诽谤**++【地质学】地势，地相**++[罕用语]动产**', '++What kind of personality do you think you have?**++你认为你自己具有什么样的个性。**++The mother@s personality pretypified her daughter@s.**++母亲的个性预示着女儿的个性。**++What can they tell us about your ability and personality?**++他们对你的能力和个性会说些什么？**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1337', 'personnel', '[,pɝsənɛl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=personnel', '{n.}++[总称]全体人员；全体职员；员工**++人事部门;人事科(或处等) [亦作 personnel department]**{adj.}++人员的；员工的**++有关人事的；主管人事的**', '++Such information is restricted within military personnel.**++这类情报资料仅限于在军事人员内部参阅。**++All the managerial personnel at the factory are hired on contract.**++工厂所有管理人员都是聘用的。**++Administrative personnel should also acquire some technical skills.**++管理人员也应该学几门手艺。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1338', 'persuasion', '[pɚsweʒn]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=persuasion', '{n.}++说服；劝说；劝服**++说服力；劝说的话(论点)**++坚定的信念；深信；信仰；信条**++具有特定信念(或信仰)的一派人；教派；集团；派别**++[口语]种；类；性别；阶级**++[美国英语]国籍**', '++Their persuasion has worn down her opposition.**++他们已经说服她不再反对。**++His father was reached by their persuasion at last.**++他的父亲最后终于被他们说服了。**++Even administrative regulations must be accompanied by persuasion and education.**++就是行政命令也要伴以说服教育。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1339', 'pertinent', '[pɝtnənt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pertinent', '{adj.}', '++The album list is a bag because order is not pertinent.**++因为顺序是不相关的，所以专辑列表是一个包。**++You can iterate over this list and access all pertinent information for each queue.**++可以循环遍历这个列表并访问每个队列的所有相关信息。**++More directly pertinent to the gold price is the rising premium in Tokyo for gold bars now up to $2, whereas there is usually no premium.**++与金价更加相关的是东京金条不断上涨的保险费，现在已经达到了2美金，而以前通常是没有的。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1340', 'pest', '[pɛst]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pest', '{n.}++讨厌的人(或东西)；害人虫**++有害动(植)物；害虫**++[罕用语]瘟疫；鼠疫**', '++And move over bedbugs, there@s a new pest in town, at least if you live in the Eastern United States.**++先撇开臭虫不说，现在城镇里又出现一种新害虫，至少如果你住在美国东部的话就会发现。**++"The major pest was controlled and so the farmers stopped spraying insecticides," he told SciDev.Net.**++“主要的害虫被控制了，因此农民停止了喷洒杀虫剂，”他告诉本网站说。**++The authorsargue that, unlike GM rice, ecological engineering does not undermine the independence of farmers in developing countries by relying on big business for pest control.**++作者们认为，与转基因水稻不同，生态工程不会让发展中国家的农民依赖大企业控制害虫从而损害其独立性。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1341', 'petition', '[pətɪʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=petition', '{n.}++请愿；申请；请求**++请愿书**++祈求；祈祷；祷文**++请求(或恳请)的东西**++【法律】申请书；陈情书；诉状**{vt.}++向…请愿；请求；要求：**++祈求；恳求：**{vi.}++请愿；要求；请求：**++请愿；要求；请求：**', '++These names will all be added to the petition.**++这些名字都将被添加到请愿书中。**++What options do you have to wage an effective petition effort?**++你有什么选择来进行一场有效率的请愿努力呢?**++Also, please fill out the petition below and tell us how you intend to masturbate for peace.**++并且，请填写下边的请愿，告诉我们你如何打算为和平而自我性爱。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1342', 'petty', '[pɛti]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=petty', '{adj.}++次要的；价值不大的**++小的；小规模的；一点点的**++渺小的；微不足道的；器量小的；卑劣的**++地位低下的；下级的**++无聊的；琐碎的**', '++From now I leave off all petty decorations.**++从今起我要抛弃一切琐碎的装饰。**++To support this formula meant upholding democracy and the Constitution; to oppose it seemed mean and petty.**++支持这个模式意味着维护民主和《宪法》；反对它似乎意味着卑鄙和狭隘。**++If you require a building permit, the petty official concerned will obviously get more pleasure from saying «No» than from saying «Yes».**++如果你要求一个建筑许可，这个相关的小官员将明显能从说“不”而非“是”获得更多快乐。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1343', 'photoelectric', '[,fotoɪlɛktrɪk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=photoelectric', '{adj.}', '++His declaration of the photoelectric effect made possible the eventual invention of television cameras.**++他对光电效应的阐述使电视摄像机的最终发明成为可能。**++The researchers then shone a laser on to the gold, which liberates electrons via the photoelectric effect.**++研究人员接着将一束激光照射到材料表面，通过光电效应释放出电子。**++This extension of the photoelectric effect, in which one photon knocks one electron off the edge of an atom, could make physicists reconsider when light is a wave and when it’s a particle.**++在这种光电效应的延伸中，一个光子从原子的边缘打出一个电子，这可能要使物理学家们重新考虑光在什么情况下是波，什么情况下是粒子。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1344', 'photography', '[fətɑɡrəfi]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=photography', '{n.}++摄影术**++照相；摄影**++一组照片**', '++He took to photography.**++他开始喜欢上摄影。**++The ABC of Photography;**++《摄影入门》**++Photography is a language, with its own limitations and strengths, but these are my tools, so I have to try and use them well.**++摄影是一门语言，它有着自己的限制和力量，但是这些是我的工具，所以我必须试着用好它们。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1345', 'physically', '[fɪzɪkli]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=physically', '{adv.}{adj.}++物质的；有形的；确确实实的**++自然界的；自然科学的；按自然规律的**++物理(学)的；**++身体(上)的；肉体(上)的**++肉欲的；好色的**++粗野的；激烈的**++[废语]医药的**{n.}++[美国英语]体格检查[全称 physical examination]**', '++My parents were never physically abused in all the time they were locked up, but it was a trying time, to say the least.**++我的父母在监禁的时间里从来没有受过身体上的折磨，但是至少可以说，那是一段十分艰难的时刻。**++We both went out with other people and there was never any jealousy, although I found it hard to be physically intimate with anyone else.**++我们都和别的人出去约会而从不会去妒忌，但是我发现身体上很难与其他人有亲密关系。**++Not only was I behind physically, but my mental game was off as well.**++不要说我的体能没有从前好了，就是精神上也大不如前了。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1346', 'pickle', '[pɪkl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pickle', '{n.}++(腌鱼、蔬菜等的)盐水；泡菜水；醋**++[复数]腌制食品；酸菜，泡菜(尤指酸黄瓜、腌菜)**++(清洁金属表面或木材防腐用的)稀酸浴；酸洗液**++[复数]一派胡言，胡说八道；无价值的东西**++空投鱼雷**++[英国英语]捣蛋鬼，讨厌鬼**++油封**++[俚语]脾气坏的女人；烂醉**++[口语]困境，尴尬处境；混乱**{vt.}++腌制；腌渍：**++酸洗：**++[美国俚语]葬送(机会等)；摧毁；杀害**{n.}++[苏格兰英语]**++谷粒；麦粒**++少量，少许**', '++How about some pickle juice?**++一些泡菜汁怎么样?**++A jar of pickle will contain pickled cabbage.**++泡菜坛盛放着泡菜。**++It is times like this when you question what you are living for, was it worth yelling at the guy at McDonald@s because he put pickle on your cheeseburger?**++总会有这样的时刻，当你问你是为了什么而生活，当你的芝士汉堡被一个小伙子放上泡菜之后是否值得为他尖叫？**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1347', 'pier', '[pɪr]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pier', '{n.}++桥墩,墩(区别于 abutment)**++(凸式)码头；直码头；防波堤，突堤**++【建筑学】脚柱；支柱；垂直的支承结构构件；结构底座**++候机楼登机走廊，旅客桥**++窗间墙；户间壁；扶壁**++(用以装门的)支框**++(望远镜等的)基墩**', '++We tied the boat to a pier.**++我们将小船拴在码头。**++He backed his boat away from the pier.**++他驾船倒驶离开码头。**++The truck stove in the pier of the road bridge.**++卡车撞坏了公路桥的桥墩。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1348', 'pierce', '[pɪrs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pierce', '{vt.}++刺穿；刺破；穿过：**++打动，感动：**++(寒冷、忧伤等)影响，侵彻：**++穿孔；挖洞；穿洞；钻孔： **++在(鼻、耳等身体部位)上穿孔[1997]**{vi.}++穿入;刺入;突破(有时与 to,into 或 through 连用)：**++穿入;刺入;突破(有时与 to,into 或 through 连用)：**', '++This week in our series, we talk about the presidency of Franklin Pierce.**++本周，我们继续向你讲述富兰克林.皮尔斯的总统任期。**++Crucified One, you are crucified upon my heart; and the nails that pierce your hands pierce the walls of my heart.**++钉在十字架上的人，你是钉在我的心上；穿透你双手的钉子，穿透了我的心壁。**++All night long you must sing to me, and the thorn must pierce your heart, and your life-blood must flow into my veins, and become mine.**++整个晚上，你都要对我唱歌，我的刺必须要刺穿你的心脏。 你赖以生存的鲜血必须要流进我的血管中，成为我的血。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1349', 'pilgrim', '[pɪlɡrɪm]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pilgrim', '{n.}++(在国外的)旅行者；流浪者，漫游者**++香客；朝山进香的人；朝拜圣地者，朝觐者**++修来生的人**++最初的移民；(美西部)新来移民**++[美国英语] [P-] 1620年移到美洲的英国清教徒**{vi.}++去朝圣；漫游；流浪：**++去朝圣；漫游；流浪：**', '++This was where the Pilgrim family lived: father, mother and young boy.**++这里就是朝圣者一家住的地方：父亲，母亲还有小男孩。**++And when we get to the simulators you@ll see an older version of this both at Seabrook and Pilgrim.**++当我们到达模拟器的时候，你们会看到,一个更旧的版本的在溪布鲁克和朝圣者都有的。**++We then will go to Seabrook and then Pilgrim and we@ll do various accident scenarios in their plant simulators which are as you know a replica of the control room of each of those plants.**++我们会前往希布鲁克还有朝圣者,我们会看到各种的事故场景在他们的,电站模拟器处，如你们所知，那是复制的,每一个电站的控制室。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1350', 'pineapple', '[paɪnæpl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pineapple', '{n.}++【植物】凤梨;菠萝(Ananas Sativus)**++【植物】凤梨树(Ananas comosus)**++[俚语]手榴弹；炸弹**++[俚语] 失业救济(金)**++[俚语]把头发剪得很短的男子发型**{adj.}++【植物】凤梨科(Bromeliaceae)的**', '++I like canned pineapple and peaches.**++我喜欢罐装的菠萝和桃子。**++Would you like to try our new pineapple pie or peach pie?**++要不要试试我们新推出的菠萝或是水蜜桃馅饼?**++It was basically a cheeseburger but with a slice of pineapple instead of meat.**++从根本上说，它是一种用一片菠萝代替肉片的起司汉堡。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1351', 'pious', '[paɪəs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pious', '{adj.}++虔诚的；信神的**++以宗教为口实的，以敬神为名的**++伪善的；道貌岸然的**++可嘉的，值得称赞的**++有善良意向的，好心的**++神圣的；非世俗的**++不可能实现的**++[古语]孝顺的，孝敬的**', '++It has to be said that the old Bousque woman, as old as she was, had not become pious with age, an unusual state of affairs in this part of the country.**++这得说像这个博斯克老太太这样老的人，随着年岁的增长也没有变得虔诚，在这个国家这么一个地区来讲可是件非同寻常的事。**++My one sufficient object was to greet that pious friend of mine, the Apostle Eliot, and rejoice with him over the many precious souls he hath won from heathendom!**++我唯一的目的是去问候我的一位虔诚的朋友，艾略特使徒，并和他一起欢庆他从邪教中争取过来的众多可贵的灵魂！**++That may be no more than another pious wish.**++那可能只是另一种虔诚的愿望。**');
