insert into CET6WordBook values ('1377', 'popularity', '[,pɑpjulærəti]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=popularity', '{n.}++普及；流行；通俗性；大众性**++名气；名望；讨人喜欢(或得人心、广受欢迎)的特点**++[古语]百姓，民众**', '++The new product jumped into popularity.**++新产品一下子普及开来。**++The new leader@s popularity gained over many members of the opposing party.**++新的领导人非常受人欢迎，他把反对党的许多成员都给争取了过来。**++Because despite the popularity of games on the Net, we must admit that there are still many proposals for adventure, almost 50% of the time.**++因为且不论这种交友方式在网上的普及程度，我们必须承认对于奇遇，还有很多建议，将近50%是关于时间的。**');
