insert into CET6WordBook values ('1394', 'prediction', '[prɪdɪkʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=prediction', '{n.}++预言；预测；预报**++预言(预测)的事物**', '++Without experience, you have no basis for any prediction.**++由于经验的缺乏，你的预言就缺乏根基。**++I’ll explain below how this interpolation and prediction works, but first let me show you why it is needed.**++下面我会阐明插值与预报是怎样工作的，但首先让我说明下为什么需要这些。**++There was no prediction for this earthquake, and therefore no warning. Hope in the accurate predictability of earthquakes evaporated.**++因为这场地震没有任何预报，因此也没有警告，想要准确预测地震的希望成为泡影。**');
