insert into CET6WordBook values ('1429', 'prolong', '[prəlɑːŋ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=prolong', '{vt.}++延长；拉长；拖长；延长时间；使持久：**++拖长(音节等的)发音：**++[废语]推迟 [亦作prolonggate]**', '++What factors shorten, prolong or amplify the effect of deception?**++什么因素会缩短、延长或扩张欺骗的结果？**++We know what to do to prevent infections and save or prolong lives.**++我们知道该怎么去做，来预防感染并且拯救或者延长生命。**++But this new era must not repeat or prolong the mistakes of its predecessor.**++但是这个新纪元必须不能重复或延长其前任的错误。**');
