insert into CET6WordBook values ('1455', 'puppy', '[pʌpi]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=puppy', '{n.}++小狗，幼犬**++(狐、海豹等)幼小动物**++自负的青年；呆笨的花花公子**++[复数][美国俚语]脚**', '++It tells you how to look after your new puppy.**++上面讲述了怎样照看你们的新小狗。**++But what gift meaning if he buy me a real puppy?**++但是如果他给我买了一个真的小狗，那意味着什么。**++Walking out of town, I saw a brown puppy follow three soldiers.**++走出县城，我看到一只褐色的小狗跟着三个士兵。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1456', 'purify', '[pjʊrɪfaɪ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=purify', '{vt.}++使纯净；使洁净：**++洗除罪恶；涤罪；使在道德(或礼仪)上洁净：**++精炼，提纯：**++去除；清除：**++使纯粹，使完美：**{vi.}++纯净；洁净**', '++With Truthful Communication, I purify my speech.**++我用真心交流净化我的言语。**++With Stillness, Simplicity and Contentment, I purify my body.**++我用平静、简单和满足净化我的行为。**++Potting up green plants in the house will purify the air inside.**++在房内盆栽绿色植物可以净化室内空气。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1457', 'pyjamas', '[pədʒæməz]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=pyjamas', '{n.}{adj.}++睡衣裤的**', '++Well, I think we all know what Ellen and Portia do: at night they lie next to each other in tightly buttoned-up pyjamas reading books about feminism, hairily and humourlessly.**++嗯，我想我们都知道她俩干了些什么吧：晚上她们就并挨着着躺在床上，各穿一件扣子扣紧的睡衣，在一片秀发的海洋中苦读有关女权运动的书籍。**++A family poses in front of their Christmas tree - all are dressed in pyjamas except the dad, who bizarrely appears topless!**++一家人在他们的圣诞树前摆好姿势照片——全穿睡衣，除了作爸爸的——孤伶精怪地上空装！**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1458', 'qualification', '[,kwɑlɪfɪkeʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=qualification', '{n.}++资格；合格证明，合格性**++限制，限定性条件**++(担任某种职务或行使某种权利等)必须具备的先决条件**++定性；描述**', '++They had every qualification for success.**++他们具备获得成功的各种条件。**++If any items satisfy this qualification, you add them to the body of the message.**++如果有任何条目符合这一条件，我们就将它们添加到消息体中。**++There are a few different scenarios for how database vendors deal with the qualification of their objects.**++关于数据库供应商如何处理他们的对象的资格问题，有几个不同的场景。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1459', 'qualify', '[kwɑləˌfaɪ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=qualify', '{vt.}++使有资格；使胜任：**++授权予，准予：**++描述，形容：**++限制，限定：**++使缓和，使减轻：**++改变(液体等的)浓度(或香味)：**{vi.}++取得资格；合格，胜任：**++得到许可，获准：**', '++All of us qualify.**++我们都有资格。**++She said many patients who qualify for the surgery do not get it because of problems with insurance coverage, but that may be short-sighted.**++她说很多有资格接受手术的病人由于保险责任范围的问题不能接受手术，但那可能是一种短视行为。**++As you can see, you now have not only specified your target namespace, but also created a namespace value PO to qualify the schema and included the documentation annotation from the example.**++正如您看到的，现在您不仅指定了目标的命名空间，而且还建立了一个命名空间值PO来限制模式和其中包含的来自示例的注解文档。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1460', 'qualitative', '[kwɑlətetɪv]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=qualitative', '{adj.}', '++Consciousness, if what we mean by consciousness is this qualitative aspect of our mental life, consciousness remains a pretty big mystery.**++如果我们所说的意识,就是指我们心理活动定性的方面,那么意识还是一个很大的谜团**++Regardless of whether a KPI is qualitative or quantitative in nature, all KPIs need to say something useful about the running of the business.**++不管 KPI 本质上是定性的还是定量的，所有的 KPI 都需要能够展现出一些有关业务运转的有用信息。**++At the end of each of the three study years, we performed quantitative evaluations of intervention coverage and provider costs, as well as qualitative assessments of the CDI process.**++在为期三年研究中，我们在每年末都开展了干预措施覆盖范围和供应商成本的定量评估，还针对CDI过程开展定性评估。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1461', 'quantify', '[kwɑntɪfaɪ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=quantify', '{vt.}++确定…的数量；用数量表示；测量，计量；量化(把质的变为量的)：**++【逻辑学】(在命题中)用量词(all， some等)加以限定**++【军事】估算**', '++How would you quantify it?**++你会如何量化呢？**++If you quantify how much they relate, then you could look at the correlation.**++如果你可以量化二者有多相关,那你就可以考察相关性了**++You business people on the team need to try your best to quantify -- in dollars -- the business value of each feature (or more likely each set of features) you ask for.**++您团队的业务人员要求您尽力量化（用美元计）您要求的每个特性（或更可能是每组特性）的商业价值。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1462', 'quantitative', '[kwɑntətetɪv]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=quantitative', '{adj.}++量的，数量(上)的**++(能)用数量表示的；能测量的**++【化学】定量的**++【语言学】音量的**++(诗)由长短音节组成的**', '++And, he needed to get quantitative.**++他需要得到定量的因素。**++While I do not present any quantitative data on speed, the chart is arranged in order of speed, from fastest to slowest.**++在速度方面，虽然我没有定量的数据，但这张表是按照速度顺序来安排的，从最快到最慢。**++For this reason, we have included our track record and the other quantitative data in this submission as an additional annex so that you can assess it on a comparable basis.**++由于这个原因，我们已在这次提交材料的附录中包括了我们的跟踪误差以及其它定量数据，这样，你就能在一个比较的基础上进行评估。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1463', 'quarterly', '[kwɔrtɚli]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=quarterly', '{adj.}++按季度的；一年四次的**++四分之一的**++(盾面等)分成四部分的**{adv.}++按季度地**++四等分地**{n.}++季刊**', '++Quarterly reports come and go, but Greece will never repay these debts.**++季度报告来来去去，而希腊是不会偿还这些债务的。**++The Quarterly: What does all this mean for managers at nonfinancial companies?**++季刊：所有这些对非金融公司的管理者们意味着什么？**++Writing in The Quarterly Review of Biology, the scientists conclude that "evidence for a role of climate in the dynamics [of malaria] is robust".**++这组科学家在《生物学评论季刊》上得出结论说：“关于气候在疟疾动力学方面的作用的证据是坚实的”。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1464', 'quartz', '[kwɔrts]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=quartz', '{n.}', '++The quartz watch keeps good time.**++石英表走时准。**++To this class of substance belong mica, porcelain, quartz, glass, wood, etc.**++属于这类物质的有云母、瓷器、石英、玻璃、木材等等。**++A quartz wristwatch, by comparison, is sensitive to about a millionth of a degree, or 10-6 degrees.**++相比而言，一个石英手表敏感度大概是一度的百万分之一，或是10-6度。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1465', 'quench', '[kwɛntʃ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=quench', '{vt.}++扑灭，熄灭：**++压倒；压制：**++满足；使缓和：**++【冶金学】淬火；使骤冷**{vi.}++熄灭；停止；平静：**++熄灭；停止；平静：**', '++Check out these three videos and quench your thirst for techno-destruction.**++看看这三个视频，平息一下你那摧毁科技的渴望吧。**++"Quench not the Spirit," Paul says in one place, and in another "grieve not the holy Spirit of God.**++“不要熄灭圣灵的感动”，保罗曾说过这句话，他也说过另一句“不要让上帝的圣灵为你忧伤”。**++Then the men of David sware unto him, saying, Thou shalt go no more out with us to battle, that thou quench not the light of Israel.**++当日，跟随大卫的人向大卫起誓说，以后你不可再与我们一同出战，恐怕熄灭以色列的灯。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1466', 'quest', '[kwɛst]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=quest', '{n.}++寻找；探索；追求**++(中世纪骑士的)远征**++中世纪参加远征的骑士**++[罕用语]验尸陪审团**{vi.}++(猎犬等)跟踪搜寻：**++探索；追求：**{vt.}++建筑；探索**', '++They are using a new prospecting method to quest for oil.**++他们正在采用一种新的勘探方法寻找石油。**++But it is indeed because he loves them with the same passion and each time with his whole self that he must repeat his gift and his profound quest.**++然而，他的确是怀有同样的激情，每次全身心地爱她们，正是因为如此，他必须重复着他的天赋和那种深邃的感情追求。**++Make it part of your quest for better health.**++让它成为你对健康追求的一部分吧。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1467', 'question', '[kwɛstʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=question', '{n.}++询问，发问**++疑问，问题**++怀疑；不肯定，无把握**++(法庭上的)争议；争论；争端**++(有待探讨的)问题**++难处**++(待辩论或表决的)提案，议题 **++(议题等的)提请表决**{vt.}++询问；质问；审讯：**++怀疑；对…表示异议：**++探究，研究：**', '++He deliberated with them over that question.**++他和他们商量了那个问题。**++After answering his question,she asked back.**++回答他的问题之后，她反问他。**++Do you realize the importance of this question?**++你意识到这个问题的重要性吗?**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1468', 'questionable', '[kwɛstʃənəbl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=questionable', '{adj.}++可疑的**++(品德等)有问题的**++不可靠的**', '++The use of the above rules is questionable, as they all could be rewritten without using any substitution operators.**++上面规则的使用都比较可疑,因为他们都可以通过不使用任何替换操作符来重写.**++What we have done is discovered some questionable activity on the execution of our script, then prepared our script to give us some understandable feedback.**++我们所做的操作是发现了执行脚本时出现的一些可疑操作，然后调整脚本使其给我们提供一些可理解的反馈。**++Leave issues of some questionable magazines out in the open.**++把一些可疑的期刊杂志摊开放在外面。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1469', 'questionnaire', '[ˌkwɛstʃənɛr]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=questionnaire', '{n.}++[法语]**++调查表(手写或印刷的表格，上有供调查用的一组问题)；征求意见表**++通过调查表进行的调查**', '++I have posted that questionnaire for you to copy and complete.**++我已经发布的问卷供您复制和填答。**++These patients agreed to complete a questionnaire about their sexual behavior and alcohol and drug use.**++这些患者同意去完成一张关于他们性行为和酒精、药物使用的调查表。**++During this second session, volunteers were given the same questionnaire as in the first, with one small difference.**++在第二次研究期间，志愿者拿到的是和第一次相同的问卷，只有一小处不同。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1470', 'quiver', '[kwɪvɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=quiver', '{vi.}++颤抖；战栗：**++颤抖；战栗：**{vt.}++使颤抖；抖动：**++使颤抖；抖动：**{n.}++颤抖；颤声**++一闪**{n.}++箭筒；箭囊**++箭囊中的箭**{adj.}', '++As he speaks, he massages his temples with fingers that quiver slightly with exhaustion.**++说话时，可以看到他略显疲惫的用颤抖的手指按摩太阳穴。**++Billions penetrate every square centimetre of the Earth’s surface every second without so much as a quiver. This makes them rather hard to detect.**++在每秒钟时间里，会有数十亿中微子穿过每平方厘米地球表面，而不会引起任何震动，这令它们很难被发现。**++Adam and Eve as the divine groom and bride is one Biblical arrow in the quiver of same-sex union opponents.**++作为神圣的新郎和新娘，在同性婚姻对手们的颤抖中，亚当和夏娃是一支《圣经》之箭。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1471', 'radial', '[redɪəl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=radial', '{adj.}++光线的；射线的**++放射状的；辐射的**++半径的；径向的**++【解剖学】桡骨的；桡骨附近的**++【动物学】射出状的(肢体，如海星等)**{n.}++光线；射线；放射结构**++桡部**++径向帘布(层)轮胎，子午线轮胎( = radial tyre)**++径向线**++【解剖学】桡神经；桡动脉**++【航空学】位置方位线；【航海学】径向线；辐射(位置)线**++星形发动机(=radial engine)**', '++Note that this is a radial gradient, whereas earlier you saw a linear gradient.**++注意，这是一个放射状渐变，而此前您看到的是一个线性渐变。**++Radial gorges extend outward from the crater, especially in the east and southeast.**++放射状的峡谷从陨石坑向外延伸，尤其在东部和东南部。**++Next in two new layers, draw a couple of Radial Gradients from white to transparency, one larger than the other.**++下一步在两个新图层中，绘制一组白色到透明的光线梯度，逐步扩大。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1472', 'radiant', '[redɪənt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=radiant', '{adj.}++光芒四射的**++明亮的，光辉灿烂的**++喜悦的；光彩的**++辐射的，放射的**{n.}++发光的物体；发热的物体**++【天文学】(流星)辐射点**', '++With Mindfulness clear and radiant, I purify my mind.**++我用清晰的光芒四射的智慧净化我的思想。**++@I think you need to take care of your skin,@ he says, @make it more radiant.**++“我认为你需要照顾好你的皮肤，”他说，“让它更加容光焕发。**++One of the best ways to make your face look more radiant is to boost your smile with an instant teeth whitener.**++让你的脸看起来更光芒四射的最佳方法之一是，使用速效牙齿增白剂，给你的笑容添彩。**');
