insert into CET6WordBook values ('1560', 'retort', '[rɪtɔrt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=retort', '{vt.}++反驳，回嘴：**++反击；进行报复：**{vi.}++反驳；顶嘴：**++反击；报复**{n.}++反驳；顶嘴**++反击；报复行动**{n.}++曲颈瓶**++蒸馏罐**{vt.}++蒸馏；干馏**', '++The night before, he had imagined the reaction of the girl and her female allies to his message, and had composed an eloquent retort to throw at these petty-minded women.**++昨天晚上，他曾经想象女孩和她的支持者们对他的留言会有怎样的反映，还为反驳这些心地狭窄的女人构思出雄辩的腹稿。**++Tune in to your partner when they talk instead of thinking about your next retort.**++当你的另一半讲话的时候，要听进去，不要去想着你下一轮的反驳。**++Pakistanis retort by complaining their country is not getting enough credit for putting these men on trial, even as some of them recognize more could have been done.**++巴基斯坦方面反驳，他们抱怨将这些人送上了法庭却没能得到应有的赞扬，虽然他们中的一些人认识到他们能做的还有很多。**');
