insert into CET6WordBook values ('1653', 'shortage', '[ʃɔrtɪdʒ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=shortage', '{n.}++不足，缺乏**++不足的数额，短缺的量**', '++Harry deserted during the food shortage.**++哈里在食物缺乏时逃亡了。**++Another is a shortage of land and freshwater for use in aquaculture.**++另一个障碍是用于水产养殖的土地和淡水资源不足。**++This shift can be complex, expensive and there is no shortage of opponents to the change.**++这种转变是复杂的、昂贵的，而且从来不缺少这种变革的反对者。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1654', 'shortcut', '[ʃɔrt,kʌt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=shortcut', '{n.}++捷径，近路**++省力省时的办法，快捷之法**++被剪短的东西(尤指烟草)**{adj.}++提供捷径的；有近路的**++有简便方法的**++被切短的**', '++They blundered when they tried to take a shortcut.**++他们企图走捷径时犯了大错。**++The best shortcut, in this case, is no shortcut at all.**++在这个例子里，最快的捷径就是不走任何捷径。**++If the class has a no-args constructor, and you want to use that constructor and then immediately invoke a single instance method on it, there@s a shortcut.**++如果该类具有一个无参构造函数，您想使用这个构造函数，然后立即在其上调用一个实例方法，那么有一种捷径。**');
