insert into CET6WordBook values ('1890', 'timely', '[taɪmli]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=timely', '{adj.}++及时的；适时的，合时宜的**++[古语] = early**{adv.}++及时地**++[古语]早**', '++The pain worked off because he received timely treatment.**++由于得到及时治疗，他的疼痛逐渐消失了。**++Risk, by itself, will not threaten the success of a project if it is recognized and addressed in a timely fashion.**++如果风险自身被公认为一种适时的方式的话，那么它将不会对项目的成功构成威胁。**++Decisions are timely when they can be successfully applied to an existing situation -- that is, before events carry an organization on beyond either acceptance or correction of that situation.**++当决策被成功地应用到现有的情况中时它们应该是及时的 —— 就是说，在事件超出了组织控制之前，要么接受要么调整形势。**');
