insert into CET6WordBook values ('1916', 'transverse', '[trænsvɝs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=transverse', '{adj.}++横的；横向的；横切的；横断的**++(笛子)横吹的[参较 end-blown]**++【数学】贯轴的**{n.}++横向梁；横断面；横向物**++【几何学】贯轴,横轴 ( = transverse axis)**++[亦作 transverse muscle]【解剖学】横肌**++【航海学】 = web frame**', '++To make a fibre vibrate in a transverse fashion, like the strings on a musical instrument, a more complex architecture is required.**++要使纤维像乐器的弦那样发生横向振动，则需要一种更为复杂的结构。**++Acoustic instruments on the submarine told us that there was a ridge at the bottom of the ocean, sitting transverse to the flow of ice.**++潜艇上的声波仪器告诉我们，在海洋底部有一道海脊，横向坐落在冰流方向上。**++Both Baddha Konasana and Upavistha Konasana unlock the sacroiliac joint and potentially strain the transverse ligaments of the sacrum, particularly if you bend forward.**++束角式和坐角式，同样会打开骶髂关节之“锁”，前屈时也向骶骨周围的横向韧带增加了潜在压力。**');
