insert into CET6WordBook values ('1949', 'underline', '[ʌndəlaɪn]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=underline', '{vt.}++在…下面画线：**++强调，加强；表明…的重要性：**{n.}++画在字行下面的横线；底线**++(书刊等)插图下面的说明**++【计算机】下画线，底线**', '++Write this down and underline it.**++写下它并且强调它。**++And, secondly, we need to underline the need for the government to take leadership on these issues.**++其次是我们有必要强调，政府必须在处理这些问题时发挥领导作用。**++This text includes different colors and font modification, such as underline, strikeout, bold, and italic text.**++该文本包含不同的颜色和字体修饰，比如下划线、删除线、粗体和斜体。**');
insert into CET6WordBook values ('1950', 'undertake', '[,ʌndɚtek]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=undertake', '{vt.}++从事；着手，开始进行：**++同意，答应；约定：**++许诺；保证：**++担任(工作等)；接受(任务等)；承担：**++负责；掌管：**{vi.}++[古语]担保；负责**++[口语]承办丧事**', '++We could undertake the work for the time being.**++我们可以暂时从事这项工作。**++Who will undertake responsibility for this work?**++谁将承担这项工作的责任?**++Do not undertake a project unless you can implement it.**++不要承担一项计划，除非你能完成这项计划。**');
