insert into CET6WordBook values ('1952', 'underwear', '[ʌndɚwɛr]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=underwear', '{n.}', '++She wants to have her hair teased and buy underwear for her grandchildren.**++她想买把她的头发打扮一下并为她的孙子买些内衣物。**++She’s almost naked now but keep her underwear on for another minute or so.**++虽然她现在已经基本裸体了但让她还穿着内衣一两分钟。**++Next time you go shopping for underwear, give some thought to what color you choose.**++下次去添置内衣时，不妨想想你通常选择什么颜色的内衣。**');
