insert into CET6WordBook values ('1985', 'ventilate', '[vɛntɪlet]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=ventilate', '{vt.}++使通风，使换气：**++给…安装通风设备**++公开谈论；发表：**++【医学】使血液吸收氧气，给…供氧**++【医学】使换气；为(病人)做人工呼吸**', '++Open the window and ventilate the room.**++打开窗户，让房间空气流通。**++Ventilate as much as possible to completely air out the room or spill zone with outside air.**++尽可能地通风，以彻底用室外空气置换房间或泄漏区域的空气。**++Safety officials said it would take at least 96 hours to ventilate the mine of deadly methane gas to make it safe for search crews to enter.**++安全官员们说，要给弥漫着甲烷这种致命气体的矿井通风至少96小时，救援人员才能安全下井搜救。**');
