insert into CET6WordBook values ('2077', 'yearn', '[jɝn]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=yearn', '{vi.}++渴望；向往，想念：**++深深感动，怜悯，同情：**', '++The man who has everything is in some way is a poor man. He will never know what it feels like to yearn, to hope, to nourish his soul with the dream of something better.**++一个拥有一切的人在某些方面也是个穷人，他永远不会知道什么是渴望、什么是期待；永远不知道用渴求更美好的东西来充实他的灵魂。**++Yet we all yearn for that deep connection with others, those moments of bliss, joy, completeness.**++然而，我们都渴望与别人深入的交往, 渴望那些幸福、快乐、圆满的时刻。**++There is nothing mysterious about this; in every aspect of life, we yearn for things to be regular and parallel.**++这点没有任何神秘的；生活中的每一方面，我们都渴望事物是有规律和对等的。**');
